陣 有冇諗到呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc579e3cd51986408b57432f7c9258855cbd3720","tid":1006711,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"學某大陸官話齋，你去過中國未，你認識中國嗎，你係咪收咗外國錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8d7779c3aed1cb0b33b74c87d3f2d6c7542a39","tid":1006711,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落難先講返人話"}]}